1. Để connect được nodejs với mysql thì cần cài đặt package mysql2
    npm install --save-exact mysql2@2.3.3
    https://www.npmjs.com/package/mysql2

2. Tạo data fake
    -  Connect vao database su dung dbeaver
    - Tao table users:
        CREATE TABLE Users(
            id int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
            email varchar(255),
            name varchar(255),
            city varchar(255)
        );
    - Tao du lieu fake  
        INSERT INTO Users 
            Values(1, 'adam@gmail.com', 'Pham Hong Hai', 'Ha Noi');

3. Connect Nodejs voi database
    viet code test trong file server.js. sau nay se tach ra theo mo hinh MVC sau

    - Import mysql2 vao file server.js
        const mysql = require('mysql2');
    - Tao connection
        const connection = mysql.createConnection({
            host: 'localhost',
            port: 3307,
            user: 'root',
            password: '123456',
            database: 'hoidanit'
        });
    - Query lay du lieu
        connection.query(
            'SELECT * FROM `Users` WHERE `id` >= 1',
            function (err, results, fields) {
                console.log(" >>>> results = ", results); // results contains rows returned by server
                console.log(">>> fields =", fields); // fields contains extra meta data about results, if available
            }
        );
    - Xem ket qua trong console log

4. Sau khi test xong thi se  khai bao config db trong file .env
    